# Codex Context Exclusions
# Large documentation files that cause context overflow in Codex proxy
docs/pr-guidelines/correctness-validation-checklist.md
docs/pr-guidelines/*/guidelines.md
*.large.md

# Large generated documentation
docs/pr-guidelines/*.md
# But allow small summaries
!docs/pr-guidelines/*summary.md
!docs/pr-guidelines/*issues.md

# Hook system artifacts (only relevant for hook development)
.codexplus/hooks/
.claude/hooks/

# Test artifacts and logs
*.log
*.pid
/tmp/codex_plus/

# Virtual environment and dependencies
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc